    <h2 id="item-price" style="color: var(--matrix-green);"></h2>
    <button class="btn-buy" onclick="initiatePayout()">BUY NOW (SECURE PAYOUT)</button>
    <p style="font-size: 10px; margin-top: 15px;">*Proceeds automatically clear municipal bills.</p>
