<footer class="footer-legal">
    <strong>CONFIDENTIALITY & LEGAL NOTICE:</strong> This portal is a protected private server of GNAIAAAC LLC. If you have accessed this garage tour by mistake, please exit immediately. Unauthorized use of data or illegal search is strictly prohibited under municipal and state law. All transactions are audited by the <strong>AI Sleeping Agent Black Box</strong> to prevent fraud and money laundering. Protected under Civil Liberties & Privacy Protection Acts. <br><br>
    &copy; 2026 SSGPT6 | Architect: Arifur Shanta. All Rights Reserved.
</footer>

<script>
    function showItem(name, price, desc) {
        document.getElementById('item-name').innerText = name;
        document.getElementById('item-price').innerText = price;
        document.getElementById('item-desc').innerText = desc;
        console.log("[AI SLEEPING AGENT]: Analyzing asset " + name);
